OL,10,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,11,     FObservational documentary series.
OL,12,     FCops from North and West Yorkshire
OL,13,     Fare cracking down on uninsured
OL,14,     Fdrivers whose recklessness is a
OL,15,     Fcost to all of us.
OL,16,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,17,     FThe interceptors make an early
OL,18,     Fhour dash to catch a team of late
OL,19,     Fnight burglars and one of the
